               stealing 13 linen shirts, value 30 s. 5 pair of linen sheets, value 30 s. 10 linen table-cloths, value 30 s. 1 linen shaving cloth, value 12 d. 14 linen towels, value 5 s. and 8 linen napkins, value 5 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17660219-2-victim42" type="victimName">
