               receiving 3 table cloths, 2 napkins, 7 towells, 2 shifts, 1 shirt, and 1 apron, part of the said goods, well knowing them to have been stolen
            </rs>, <rs id="t17660219-2-cd13" type="crimeDate">December 17</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17660219-2-off7 t17660219-2-cd13"></join>
